{"tid":1305034,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你，點解要去光復上水、沙田遊行呀","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T05:30:39.000Z","uid":79957,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9dd289e2084b40245ace67d131dda7a1ec3f101","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"對唔住係我標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但答案好撚簡單：<br />\n沙田遊行係和理非回合，用嚟聚返和理非人氣，議題上對準訴求；前線勇武可以休息下嘅階段<br />\n<br />\n但上水遊行就<strong>肯撚定唔係和理非回合</strong><br />\n好似隔離post咁講，大家唔嚟幫手，就等於推自己人去死呀<br />\n<br />\n我明好多人講主線支線<br />\n但而家聚焦又咁散，<br />\n反而上水係代表槍頭對準中共；<br />\n沙田係代表和理非民意reassemble<br />\n呢d支線做得好係可以幫到主線好大忙<br />\n屌你地明唔明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26b9295784440e2f17bb72d2a74b435e5b48214","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:39:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"350e577be2e5aae196584b230e6954723b878834","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c6e28c7180fd0cb0b196d1eb072526aa7d5315b","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:42:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2876b97c88521931791f244d71de380e98775586","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:45:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"530cb1df968dc738de118c735bf7b359b08f89d3","tid":1305034,"uid":138212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:29:04.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"9ce36aee02dd9500b3981364c8003161db04e784","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T20:47:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5acebbb56ab87ef525136311b3a7e539fd74e5b","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:29:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17c9e0fda23dc96da07b577812da59ff3d5607c9","tid":1305034,"uid":46822,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:49:40.000Z","msg":"去上水沙田政府根本唔驚你<br />\n好似屯門咁，屯公d雞做少一日生意有咩所謂<br />\n反而圍中環港交所、IFC 等等仲實際，講緊個度d公司生意係每日億億聲<br />\n戴妖當年既&rdquo;佔中&rdquo; 根本就未真係實現到"},{"pid":"ed29512b9088f484b2e897964bc529e284487d6e","tid":1305034,"uid":8532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T21:52:13.000Z","msg":"我都同意<br />\n幾次政府出黎解話，都係大遊行/針對5大訴求既遊行<br />\n<br />\n光復係有助民生，但政府唔會理<br />\n所以可以遲少少再做"},{"pid":"2cc564f7437df2efd2ed7f2eaa38109afc43dcb2","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:40:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bca13df954ffae69e76492c34c9b6c3c68034cd7","tid":1305034,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3725089f6ed53ef49bcc87240015863db4a1293","tid":1305034,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n<br />\n我而家係公民拘捕你，因為你對我朋友施以實質傷害的襲擊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n然後幾個一齊撲上去<br />\n各位識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c9082a64927d1e6a152d530f160ef122ba4241","tid":1305034,"uid":79957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3725089f6ed53ef49bcc87240015863db4a1293","tid":1305034,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:37:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">立即停手，我而家嚴重警告你，唔好再襲擊<br />\n<br />\n我而家係制止你再打人，請立即停手<br />\n<br />\n我而家係公民